OL,12,Fconvert a 1700s stone cottage in
OL,13,FLlandovery into a self-catering
OL,14,Fholiday let in 2003.
OL,16,FThey hoped it would give them an
OL,17,Fincome after retiring from the
OL,18,Fmilitary and the NHS.
