OL,3,CSecond home policy 'harming genuine
OL,4,Choliday let businesses' warns expert
OL,6,FBut Mr MacGill said the t in April
OL,7,F2023 are "a blanket, one size fits all
OL,8,Fstrategy", with bills rocketing.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government hopes to tackle
OL,11,Fthe housing crisis in areas with high
OL,12,Frates of second home ownership.
OL,14,FHoliday let businesses must now be let
OL,15,Fout for 182 days a year, or six
OL,16,Fmonths, to qualify for business tax.
OL,18,FIf not, it could be classed as a
OL,19,Fsecond home meaning the owners could
OL,20,Fpay a council tax premium - up to 300%
OL,21,Fin some parts of Wales.
