OL,6,F"We feel we're being targeted, almost
OL,7,Fdiscrimination against. You know it's
OL,8,Fa one size fits all solution. It's a
OL,9,Fblanket strategy in order to challenge
OL,10,Fthe housing problems we've got."
OL,12,FAround 3,000 self-catering businesses
OL,13,Fin Wales have been adjusting to the
OL,14,Fpolicy changes.
OL,16,FAlistair Handyside, chair of the
OL,17,FProfessional Association of Self
OL,18,FCaterers, spends his time supporting
OL,19,Fholiday let business owners with their
OL,20,Fmental health.
