OL,6,F"It's a massive stress point. You
OL,7,Fwouldn't say to a pub that they need
OL,8,Fto sell a certain number of pints or
OL,9,Ffor hotels to book a certain number of
OL,10,Frooms," Mr Handyside said.
OL,12,FHe continued: "It's an artificial
OL,13,Fmeasure which most Welsh businesses in
OL,14,Fself catering cannot meet.
OL,16,F"We understand the Welsh Government
OL,17,Fhas objectives but don't harm genuine
OL,18,FWelsh businesses. This particular
OL,19,Fmeasure is the most harmful of them
OL,20,Fall."
